{"title":"校园邮箱账号获取","time":"2022 年 8 月 20 日","shareable":true,"id":"guide/account/mail/get","author":"Mr.Hope","cite":[],"content":[{"tag":"ul","type":"info","text":["对于 2021 级及之前的同学们，邮箱账号是学校默认分配的，其格式为 “姓全拼 + 名首字母缩写 + 三位数字序号”。","对于 2022 级及之后的同学们，邮箱账号是自行申请的。","对于本科在东师就读的同学们，研究生阶段使用同一个邮箱，学校不会额外分配新邮箱。"]},{"tag":"text","text":["如果你忘记了你的邮箱账号，你可以通过以下流程获得邮箱。"]},{"tag":"title","text":"2022 级及之后"},{"tag":"text","text":["1. 登录网上服务大厅"]},{"tag":"action","header":"校内访问","content":"https://my.nenu.edu.cn/"},{"tag":"action","header":"校外访问","content":"https://my.webvpn.nenu.edu.cn/"},{"tag":"text","text":["2. 进行如下选择"]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail-apply1.png"},{"tag":"text","text":["3. 找到“个人邮箱申请”入口。"]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail-apply2.png"},{"tag":"text","text":["4. 点击开始办理"]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail-apply3.png"},{"tag":"text","text":["5. 系统会提示分配的邮箱账户名称"]},{"tag":"img","src":"https://mp.innenu.com/img/account/mail-account-hint.png"},{"tag":"title","text":"2021 级及之前"},{"tag":"text","text":["1. 请先完成“东北师范大学”企业微信认证。"]},{"tag":"list","header":false,"items":[{"text":"企业号认证","icon":"apply","path":"guide/account/wechat/authorize"}]},{"tag":"text","text":["2. 下载企业微信 App 并完成登录。"]},{"tag":"action","header":"安卓下载企业微信","content":"https://work.weixin.qq.com/wework_admin/commdownload?platform=android&from=wwindex"},{"tag":"action","header":"iOS 下载企业微信","content":"https://work.weixin.qq.com/wework_admin/commdownload?platform=ios&from=wwindex"},{"tag":"text","text":["3. 请通过微信登陆企业微信","4. 在侧边栏中选择“东北师范大学”机构","5. 点击下方 Tab 栏中的 “工作台”","6. 在工作台中找到“个人中心”并进入","7. 点击个人中心下方菜单栏中的 “信息查询”-“人员信息”"]}]}